Our team took a trip to Sedona using the #Xperia1III by @sonyxperia @sonyxperiaus. With four versatile lenses (from ultrawide to tele), we captured every moment at the drop of a hat. 

From sunrise to sunset, we utilized the phone just like we would an Alpha camera by Sony, and it did not disappoint. 

Having a device with these capabilities that fits in your pocket, is a game changer. It’s portable while still remaining professional. 

#artofvisuals #Xperia1III #SonyXperia #MobilePhotography #MobileVideography #TravelByXperia #TakenWithXperia #Sedona

Introducing a new camera that will change the way we see, capture and create – the Sony Alpha 1. ‘Hunters of Light’, presented by Sony Alpha films, celebrates those who search for the things that have yet to exist, who challenge traditions, and who see as others do not. 

"Now let us write together…a new chapter." 

By @sonyalpha films

Featuring members of our #AlphaFamily: Kesha Lambert @keshalambert Jose Silva (@jnsilva) Cristina Mittermeier (@mitty), Paul Nicklen (@paulnicklen), Charly Savely (@charlysavely), Phil Yoon (@phil.yoon), Philip Edsel (@edsel). Directed by Curtis Morgan (@curtismorgan).

Our favorite camera release of 2020 was without a doubt @sonyalpha's a7SIII. 
We wanted to see if it was capable of shooting a full-scale commercial usually reserved for much larger cameras. We recently teamed up with @sony to creat a spot for the new Sony WH-1000XM4 headphones. The results blew us away. With features like an updated menu, refreshed ergonomics, updated color science, and 10-bit color, this camera is an obvious choice and a near-perfect upgrade for anyone doing video production. 

The Sony a7SIII is now in stock at adorama.com - click the link to learn more:
https://www.adorama.com/isoa7sm3c.html

In Partnership with @adorama #SonyAlpha #CreateNoMatterWhat #Sony #ThisMoment

The @sony WH-1000XM4 headphones take you even deeper into silence - which we could all benefit from and utilize in our beautifully chaotic lives. 

Sony’s WH-1000XM4 headphones feature premium sound that elevates your listening experience with the ability to personalize and control everything you hear with smart listening that adjusts to your situation.

Not only are these headphones designed for comfort, but their exceptional battery life, speak-to-chat function, and multi-device connection ability leave them unmatched in the marketplace.

These headphones are our top choice for creators looking to have a moment of serenity. 

Click the link below to learn more.
https://www.sony.com/electronics/headband-headphones/wh-1000xm4

Detailed Specs:
- HD Noise-Canceling Processor QN1, Bluetooth Audio SoC and a dual noise sensor let you listen without distractions
- Personal noise canceling optimizer and atmospheric pressure optimizing
- High-quality audio with DSEE Extreme™ and LDAC
- Adaptive Sound Control automatically adjusts ambient sound settings to suit your location and behavior
- Wireless freedom with BLUETOOTH® technology

In Partnership with @sony @artofvisuals #SonyAudio #SonyHeadphones #ThisMoment

Feeling overwhelmed should not be the norm, but it's a feeling we can all relate to. When the world gets noisy, headphones aren't just a piece of tech - they're a device for creating an environment, a moment of peace and serenity no matter where you are or what may be happening around you. We've teamed up with @sony to highlight this moment - this moment is for you. 

We've always been big fans and users of Sony's audio line, so we're excited to showcase their new WH-1000XM4 Wireless Noise-Canceling Headphones. With industry leading noise cancellation, premium sound quality, and complete wireless freedom, the Sony WH-1000XM4s are a great companion for creating tranquility in a noisy world.  

We're thrilled to share this project that we've been working on alongside @karl_shakur @erubes1 @audriestorme. Our goal has always been and will always be to inspire the creator community. Be on the lookout for a full gear highlight & more. 

In Partnership with @sony @artofvisuals #SonyAudio #SonyHeadphones #ThisMoment

Enjoy!

As creatives, it's important that we take time to get outside of our everyday life and explore new ways to create. There’s no better time than now to creatively explore and learn new skills. Regardless of where you live or what gear you have, we want you to Create No Matter What. We have teamed up with amazing partners to bring you another video challenge!

The sixth Create No Matter What challenge is all about capturing action in video with the theme 'Go with the Flow.' We want to see all the action whether you use footage you've been sitting on or you go out and shoot something this week. Submit your videos for a chance to win a prize package worth over $3000! 

Submit your videos: https://bit.ly/2Z2jSsG

The deadline for submissions is ‪August 5, 2020 at 11:59 PM ET‬. The winner will be announced ‪on August 7th at 12 noon‬ ET. Make sure to also post your videos on your social and use #CreateNoMatterWhat and #Adorama! We can't wait to see what you capture!

3.2 instillation by @404.zero at @dark_mofo, Hobart, Tasmania, June 2021

Our first experience of a complete remotely produced large-scale installation. The whole setting up went surprisingly smooth without any issue thanks to the highly professional Dark Mofo crew. 
The entire audiovisual content was produced before real setting up - we spent two weeks in a warehouse in Saint Petersburg with a similar sound system, full tables of modular synthesizers, and visualizer. 
It was a new experience for us - never had the ability to deeply focus on sound and light for such a large-scale setup rather than counting hours before running the show.

So great thanks to Dark Mofo for believing in us!
And great thanks to our local friends for tech support during the preparation of the content: @sevcableport, @setupdesigns, @tokimprovisation

node.text:
Our team took a trip to Sedona using the #Xperia1III by @sonyxperia @sonyxperiaus. With four versatile lenses (from ultrawide to tele), we captured every moment at the drop of a hat. 

From sunrise to sunset, we utilized the phone just like we would an Alpha camera by Sony, and it did not disappoint. 

Having a device with these capabilities that fits in your pocket, is a game changer. It’s portable while still remaining professional.
